snippet.title: Wreckfest 2 | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for more mayhem! 

Wreckfest 2 is coming to PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X|S, featuring a completely overhauled physics engine for even more realistic destruction, fully customizable cars that you can share with other players and revamped game modes including a brand-new split screen mode. Wishlist now! 

- Links & Info - 
Website: wreckfest2.thqnordic.com 
Discord: discord.gg/wreckfest 
Steam: thqn.net/wf2-steam 

- Our Socials -
